<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Visit the Indus Valley Civilization</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      background-color: #f4f1e6;
    }
    header {
      background-color: #8b5e3c;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    nav {
      background-color: #c19a6b;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    nav a {
      margin: 0 15px;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    section {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    footer {
      background-color: #8b5e3c;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Explore the Indus Valley Civilization</h1>
  <p>Discover one of the world's oldest and most advanced ancient societies</p>
</header>

<nav>
  <a href="#about">About</a>
  <a href="#geography">Geography</a>
  <a href="#achievements">Achievements</a>
  <a href="#visit">Plan Your Visit</a>
</nav>

<section id="about">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>About the Civilization</h2>
    <p>The Indus Valley Civilization thrived around 2500 BCE along the Indus River. It is known for its advanced cities, organized society, and impressive innovations.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="geography">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Geography</h2>
    <p>Located near the Indus River, this region featured fertile plains perfect for farming. Seasonal flooding helped crops grow, supporting large populations.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="achievements">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Major Achievements</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Advanced city planning with grid systems</li>
      <li>Indoor plumbing and drainage systems</li>
      <li>Standardized weights and measures</li>
      <li>Early form of writing</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="visit">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Plan Your Visit</h2>
    <p>Walk through ancient cities like Mohenjo-Daro and Harappa. Experience the birthplace of urban civilization and see history come alive!</p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>Travel back in time – Visit the Indus Valley today!</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
